          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有事来通报，无事不乱言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见老夫人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。命你去到寒窑打听三姑娘，怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘在寒窑身染重病。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘在寒窑身染重病。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听得家院禀一声，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "烈性的三女病缠身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "眼望寒窑珠泪——"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "滚，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怎不叫娘痛伤心？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫人不必啼哭。何不多带钱米，去到寒窑探望三姑娘？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院、丫鬟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院、丫鬟",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多带钱米，随我探望你家三姑娘。吩咐车辆伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王夫人离座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "车辆走上！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（车夫暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王夫人哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮三眼板",
          "musical_style": "西皮三眼板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为娇儿把我的心机用尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮三眼板",
          "musical_style": "西皮三眼板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想当年大不该在彩楼招亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮三眼板",
          "musical_style": "西皮三眼板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为娇儿失却了夫妻之情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮三眼板",
          "musical_style": "西皮三眼板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到寒窑母女们细说分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王夫人、车夫、家院、丫鬟同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来到寒窑！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去叫门！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王夫人下车。车夫暗下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘开门来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听窑外有人声，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想是四邻探奴身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘开门来。老夫人来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘亲到寒窑前来做甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "思往事似钢刀刺在我心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这般的光景怎见娘亲？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏开窑门，出窑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝钏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王夫人哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见娇儿不由娘两泪淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘，母亲，娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝钏，我儿，儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王夫人哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手拉娇儿说分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "闷来花园散散心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "面黄肌瘦无精神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫娘心疼不心疼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿在那相府多由性"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自从你把寒窑进"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "千般苦处儿受尽"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘亲不必痛伤心，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女儿言来听分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "许配达官做夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "彩球单打平贵身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谁是那耕田种地的人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大姐"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二姐有福分"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "唯有宝钏的命运苦"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若世人都为宦"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我心中只把相国恨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一样的女儿两样的心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为娘言来听分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好似枯木又逢春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "回头我对宝钏论"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今日母女重相会"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲在上，待女儿大礼参拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿不要拜了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女儿久离膝下，少奉甘旨，望母亲恕女儿不孝之罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏跪拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿起来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院、丫鬟，见过你家三姑娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院、丫鬟参",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见三姑娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院、丫鬟同行礼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。母亲不在相府，来到寒窑做甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院回府报道，我儿身染重病。此病从何而起？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲有所不知。只因魏虎回朝，打从寒窑经过。是他言道，我夫平贵命丧西凉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹又差人前来，劝女儿改嫁。儿听此言，痛哭不止，因此身得重病。今日"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲到此，女儿这病么，就好了一半了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你这老天杀的！为何常常来逼女儿改嫁？此番回去，我定要与他吵闹一场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊母亲，不要为了女儿之事，伤了你二老的和气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，看在我儿分上，不与你父吵闹就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，为娘要进得窑去，看看我儿的光景如何。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寒窑窄小，不去也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，我儿住得了，难道为娘就进去不得么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，待女儿打扫打扫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要打扫，与为娘带路。儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "画阁雕梁儿不住，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "破瓦寒窑怎把身存？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏、王夫人同进窑。家院、丫鬟同随进。家院端饭碗与王夫人看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "珍馐美味儿不用，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "粗茶淡饭怎把饥充？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝钏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀，母亲哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我哭哇，哭一声宝钏儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我叫，叫一声老娘亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想当初在相府何等光景，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到如今叫为娘好不心疼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只当孩儿丧了命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母亲莫要挂在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我儿随娘相府进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "享尽荣华不愁贫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿与爹爹三击掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "饿死寒窑也不进相府的门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "王宝钏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王夫人 （同西皮摇板） 啊、啊、啊……我的（娘哪）（儿呀）！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘亲请上容儿禀："
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母女们在寒窑叙一叙苦情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女儿我后花园去把香焚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "后宫娘娘得知情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "绣成彩球定终身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谁知单打花郎身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "爹爹一见怒气生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "前门赶走——"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "薛平贵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又将女儿赶出了后门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "破瓦寒窑把身存。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "红鬃烈马乱伤人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "唐王驾前报功勋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平贵做了马前先行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿似孤雁失了群！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "莫把女儿挂在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "都只为老娘亲身染重病"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "许愿降香三年整"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恩赐五彩花绒线"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望打中宦门后"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妻二人相府进"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妻二人无投奔"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "红沙涧内妖魔现"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平贵擒了红鬃马"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "西凉贼子造了反"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一去不觉十七载"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母亲回府对父论"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我儿不必心烦闷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为娘言来听分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不要记挂平贵身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "随娘坐来伴娘行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为娘舍死把命拼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿就是披麻戴孝的人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "休与你父来争论"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿随为娘相府进"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若你父把话论"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若为娘百年后"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘亲不必泪淋淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女儿言来听分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿是披麻戴孝的人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女儿不去哭半声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他那里不把儿当人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "至死不回这相府的门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若老娘百年后"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若爹爹身亡故"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是女儿不孝敬"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "宝钏心志早已定"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "立志守节拿得稳，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "皇天不负受苦的人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若老娘百年后"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若爹爹身亡故"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是女儿不孝敬"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "宝钏心志早已定"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院、丫鬟，将带来的银米交与你家三姑娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！相府之物，女儿一概不要。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你如不要，岂不辜负为娘一片好心？儿呀，收下了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这便才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院、丫鬟，你们暂且回去。老身今日在此陪伴你家三姑娘一宵，明日回府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊母亲，寒窑如此肮脏，母亲怎能住得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿住得，难道为娘就住不得么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！母亲不回相府，这便如何是好？我自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊母亲，女儿情愿跟随母亲回转相府去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这便才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院，吩咐车辆走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿开了窑门！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏开窑门。王夫人、家院、丫鬟同出窑。王宝钏急关窑门。车夫暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀儿呀！为何将窑门关闭了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲哪！儿与爹爹三击掌，纵然饿死寒窑，也是不回相府的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王夫人哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿狠心不把娘来送，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿跪寒窑送娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "娘哭儿来天地震，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿哭娘来泪双淋！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我那狠心的宝钏儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我那疼儿的老娘亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王夫人 （同哭头） 啊、啊、啊……我的（娘啊）（儿呀）！"
